-through rates by up to 30%."}}]}. Rules: (1) Maximum 10 questions per page for rich result eligibility. (2) Questions must be complete, not truncated. (3) Answers must be complete and match the visible page content. (4) Do not use FAQ schema for customer support contact forms. (5) Each page should have unique FAQ content; do not duplicate across multiple pages.',
